---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section s3-dosage">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="s3-dosage__heading">Choose Your NAD+ Dosage</h2>

    <div class="s3-dosage__grid">

      <div class="s3-dosage__card">
        <p class="s3-dosage__dose"><strong>250mg</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__tagline">Best for first-time users, regular wellness maintenance, and a significant cognitive boost.</p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__body">Provides a significant boost to your NAD+ levels, improving energy, focus, and cellular health. Ideal for those new to NAD+ therapy or those maintaining their wellness regimen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-dosage__card">
        <p class="s3-dosage__dose"><strong>500mg</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__tagline">Best for those seeking robust anti-aging benefits, enhanced energy levels, and athletic recovery.</p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__body">Our most popular therapeutic dose, the 500mg infusion delivers a powerful surge of NAD+ to combat the effects of aging, supercharge your metabolism, and promote deep cellular repair.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s3-dosage__card">
        <p class="s3-dosage__dose"><strong>750mg</strong></p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__tagline">Best for those seeking maximum cognitive enhancement, intensive cellular repair, and longevity support.</p>
        <p class="s3-dosage__body">Our highest dosage for the most profound impact on your health and longevity. Recommended for those with specific health goals or experienced NAD+ users looking for maximum therapeutic benefit.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="s3-dosage__cta">
      <a
        href={site.calcomUrl}
        class="btn btn--primary btn--lg"
      >
        Schedule Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-dosage__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s3-dosage__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .s3-dosage__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
  }

  .s3-dosage__dose {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-dosage__tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .s3-dosage__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-dosage__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .s3-dosage__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s3-dosage__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s3-dosage__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .s3-dosage__cta .btn {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
